      <title>随着抛售加剧，全球库存指标接近超卖区域</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/global-stock-gauge-nears-oversold-zone-as-selloff-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在本月风险资产抛售之后，全球股市基准已急剧下跌至接近超卖区域。]]></description>
